:

1. *Nasamo* smo proveli ceo vikend. (We spent the whole weekend alone.)
2. Čim smo stigli *nasamo* smo se odmah umorili. (As soon as we got alone, we got tired immediately.)
3. *Nasamo* srećne uživamo u ljubavi. (We enjoy love alone happily.)
4. *Nasam* smo bili u trenutku kada smo se upoznali. (We were alone at the moment when we got to know each other.)
5. Želimo da se vratimo *nasamo* da nastavimo našu ljubav. (We want to go back alone to continue our love.)